item.description:
​
Band: Red Hot Chili Peppers
Album: The Teatro Sessions
Date: 1998/09/15
Genre: Alternative
Quality: 16bit/44.1kHz
Country: US
Size: 608.8MB


Info:The band rehearsed and recorded a session of demos for the 'Californication' album in September of 1998 at El Teatro studio in Oxnard. The tracks with Anthony's early vocals seem to be run-throughs of the more finished songs.The others are far looser, with only rough vocals or none at all. Plate of Brown, Tellin' a Lie, Mommasan, Andaman & Nicobar, Sugar Sugar, Trouble In The Pub, and Boatman were completely unheard of prior to these leaks. This also has the famous demo of the reggae version of Californication!
